		title: "Silver"
		icon: {id: "gtceu:silver_ore", Count: 1b}
		description: ["GTCEu silver veins spawn underground, often alongside lead. Used in circuits and conductive components. Also a byproduct of Galena maceration."]
		tasks: [{
